itle=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Niestandardowy:</strong> This feature is non-standard and is not on a standards track. Do not use it on production sites facing the Web: it will not work for every user. There may also be large incompatibilities between implementations and the behavior may change in the future.</p></div></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Zwraca łańcuch znaków reprezentujący kod źródłowy tablicy.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>arr</var>.toSource()</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Brak.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Metoda <code>toSource</code> zwraca następujące wartości:</p>\n\n<p><span class=\"comment\">This shouldn't be here, but until reorganization where pages are moved to their proper places, the title of this article is ambiguous, so it can stay. After reorganization, this should be removed.</span></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Dla wbudowanego obiektu <code>Array</code>, <code>toSource</code> zwraca następujący łańcuch znaków sygnalizując, że kod źródłowy jest niedostępny:\n\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>natywny kod<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n </li>\n <li>Dla instancji <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a>, <code>toSource</code> zwraca łańcuch znaków reprezentujący kod źródłowy.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Metoda ta jest zazwyczaj wywoływana wewnętrznie przez JavaScript, a nie bezpośrednio w kodzie. Możliwe jest wywołanie <code>toSource</code> podczas debugowania, aby zbadać zawartość tablicy.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad_sprawdzanie_kodu_.c5.bar.c3.b3d.c5.82owego_tablicy","title":"Przykład: Sprawdzanie kodu źródłowego tablicy","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Do sprawdzania kodu źródłowego tablicy:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> alpha <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"c\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nalpha<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toSource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//zwraca [\"a\", \"b\", \"c\"]</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toSource()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/toString\"><code>Array.prototype.toString()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Podsumowanie","id":"podsumowanie"},{"text":"Składnia","id":"sk.c5.82adnia"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przyk.c5.82ady"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce"}],"summary":"Zwraca łańcuch znaków reprezentujący kod źródłowy tablicy.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Array.prototype.toSource()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toSource()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toSource()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toSource()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toSource()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toSource()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Array.prototype.toSource()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/array/tostring","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/array/tostring/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle"